
---

## .gitignore Content (Paste this)

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
*.so
*.egg
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
*.whl
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

# Jupyter Notebooks
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb

# Markdown temp files
*.log
*.aux
*.out
*.toc

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Quarto (if ever used later)
_quarto.yml
*_files/
*.pdf
*.html

# Temporary draft files
*.draft
*.bak
